headline: Target Cautions Shareholders Regarding TRC Capital's "Mini-Tender" Offer
summary: Target Corporation (NYSE: TGT) received notice of an unsolicited mini-tender offer by TRC Capital Corporation ("TRC Capital") to purchase up to 1,500,000 shares of Target's common stock at a price of $89.00 per share in cash, without interest. The offer is for approximately 0.33 percent of the outstanding shares of Target's common stock.
